{"tid":616584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[火都嚟]老麥薯條加大應該計g!!","createTime":"2018-04-04T09:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T12:30:41.000Z","uid":126603,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a501e1e7aaaabe3408d1da86895523576c174b3f","tid":616584,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"都唔明，明明嗌咗加大，個份量比中薯條重要少<br />\n唔怪得啲人話買兩個細薯條重抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係啲想慳住啲薯條，控制成本嘅經理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n計我話老麥薯條應該計g分大/中/小，噉我加大啲錢正洗得有價值少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔係想計較多少，而係我真係食唔飽。<br />\n噉耐正食一次，加個大過吓口癮啫，你都嚟同我計到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你哋話係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f962b19dcec1aef591f96ce9a4c7aae1fb66ce66","tid":616584,"uid":15358,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:43:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/174306_7f491a57bf5e183aeec9922eb32e24eb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F174306_7f491a57bf5e183aeec9922eb32e24eb.gif&h=38668d61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"655cd9732c1f68cf610afd023a2c3813beddfd4a","tid":616584,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T10:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> pish"},{"pid":"398cb29c955f0fffd24ce1b619e557e7388ef443","tid":616584,"uid":35649,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1